2.title: Eliezer Yudkowsky
2.clickbait: Cofounder, with Nick Bostrom, of the field of value alignment theory.
2.text: Eliezer Yudkowsky is, with [18k], one of the cofounders of [2v value alignment theory].  He is the founder of the [15w].  He is the inventor of [ timeless decision theory] and [ extrapolated volition], the co-inventor with [223] of the [ tiling agents problem] that kicked off the study of [1c1], and so on and so on.  His specializations include [ logical decision theory], [ naturalistic reflection], and [adversarial_AI_safety_analysis pinpointing the failure modes] in [2c design proposals for advanced AIs].
